title: SwiftTEA: This Squirrel Is Truly Nuts!
description:
It's about time we got something *mostly* right! Taylor Swift is going to be on SNL and a few other late-night shows. What is she planning to do? Plus, more reasons this is looking like a double release. And Taylor can't just be normal for even a day... Was her Halloween costume an Easter egg?
What did we miss? What would you like to hear? There are lots of ways to contact us!
